sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as BC Administrator
    participant BC as Business Central
    participant API as BC API Layer
    participant Bridge as ERP–UNS Bridge
    participant UNS as MQTT Broker (UNS)

    note over Admin,UNS: Scenario: New Edge Node Comes Online

    Bridge->>UNS: SUBSCRIBE<br/>mb/v1/+/+/+/+/execution

    UNS-->>Bridge: MESSAGE<br/>Topic: mb/v1/nw/edge/packaging/p1/execution<br/>{ orderNo: "PO-5000", operationNo: "20", ... }

    Bridge->>API: GET /unsTopicMappings<br/>$filter=unsTopic eq 'mb/v1/nw/edge/packaging/p1'
    API-->>Bridge: 200 OK<br/>[] (empty – topic not mapped)

    note over Bridge: Topic unknown – auto-discovery flow

    Bridge->>API: POST /unsTopicMappings<br/>{ unsTopic: "mb/v1/nw/edge/packaging/p1",<br/>status: "Inactive", description: "Auto-discovered",<br/>sourceSystem: "UNS-Bridge" }
    API-->>Bridge: 201 Created

    note over Admin,UNS: Administrator Reviews New Topic

    Admin->>BC: Open UNS Topic Mapping List
    BC-->>Admin: Shows new Inactive mapping

    Admin->>BC: Assign Work Center "PACK-P1"<br/>Set Status = Active
    BC-->>Admin: Mapping saved

    note over Admin,UNS: Next Message is Processed

    UNS-->>Bridge: MESSAGE<br/>Topic: mb/v1/nw/edge/packaging/p1/execution<br/>{ orderNo: "PO-5000", operationNo: "20", ... }

    Bridge->>API: GET /unsTopicMappings<br/>$filter=unsTopic eq 'mb/v1/nw/edge/packaging/p1'
    API-->>Bridge: 200 OK<br/>[{ workCenterNo: "PACK-P1", status: "Active" }]

    Bridge->>API: POST /executionEvents<br/>{ workCenterNo: "PACK-P1", ... }
    API-->>Bridge: 200 OK

